N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 922.20 - Copies of regulations

State Regulations

The chief mechanical officer of each operator shall keep
each inspector of locomotive boilers or steam reservoirs under his supervision
supplied with a copy of this Part. Notes
